data.description: This beautiful home is located in the highly sought-after Lewisburg school district. It boasts 5 spacious bedrooms and 3 full baths, with 3 bedrooms situated on the lower level. One of the bedrooms is currently being used as an exercise room and office. The primary bedroom features a separate tub and shower, his and her closets, and a brand-new vanity with double sinks. The guest bathroom also has a new vanity. The kitchen is fully equipped with a microwave, dishwasher, refrigerator, breakfast nook, and custom cabinets. The entry leads to a formal dining room, and there's a separate laundry room with cabinets. The great room comes with a cozy fireplace and tile flooring in the kitchen and baths. The house has beautiful hardwood flooring throughout. The outdoor area is perfect for entertaining with its stunning saltwater pool and fenced backyard with a patio. There's also a 2-car attached garage. Don't miss out on the opportunity to see this incredible home for yourself, you won't be disappointed.
